These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
Music-Genre: indie, dubstep, jazz, techno
1. Music-Genre:techno is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of Music-Genre:dubstep##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:jazz is on the left or right of Music-Genre:techno##3
5. Beverage:7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Music-Genre        | indie | dubstep   | techno | jazz    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
Color: grey, emerald, aquamarine, brown
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. Color:grey is on the left of Color:aquamarine##1
3. Color:aquamarine is in an odd position##4
4. Color:grey == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. Color:emerald is on the right of Color:aquamarine##1
6. Color:grey == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Color   | brown    | grey | aquamarine | emerald    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
Transport: car, taxi, trike, bus
1. Food:watermelon is on the left or right of Transport:bus##3
2. Food:pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. Transport:bus is on the left or right of Food:grapes##3
4. Transport:bus is on the right of Transport:trike##1
5. Transport:car is in an odd position##4
6. Food:grapes is on the right of Food:pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| Transport   | trike        | bus     | car | taxi |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
