Music-Genre: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. Job:photographer is between Music-Genre:blues and Music-Genre:reggae##2
2. Job:librarian is on the left of Job:mechanic##1
3. Music-Genre:indie is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:folk is on the left of Music-Genre:reggae##1
5. Music-Genre:folk is on the right of Job:mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job         | librarian | mechanic | photographer | nurse |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

