4. Job:teacher is on the right of Movie-Genre:time-travel##1
5. Job:coach is between Job:teacher and Job:pilot##2
6. Movie-Genre:crime is in an odd position##4
7. Movie-Genre:crime is between Job:coach and Movie-Genre:comedy##2
8. Job:coach is on the left or right of Job:pilot##3

