2. Job:mechanic is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
3. Job:electrician is between Job:mechanic and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. Job:electrician is on the left or right of Job:mechanic##3
6. Beverage:cola is on the left or right of Job:nurse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
