.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: 7up, fanta, milk, water
Flower: dahlia, orchid, tulip, aconite
1. Flower:orchid is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:milk is on the left or right of Beverage:7up##3
3. Beverage:water is on the far left or far right##3
4. Flower:tulip is on the left of Flower:aconite##1
5. Flower:aconite is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
6. Flower:tulip is in an even position##4
7. Flower:dahlia == Beverage:fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
| Flower       | orchid  | tulip | aconite | dahlia  |

